# SPITBOL run-listing lines that vary between runs, builds, or machines.
# One regex per line; matching lines are dropped before golden comparison.
# Version + build banner
^macro spitbol version
^x86-64 .*\d{4}$
# Listing page header
^\s*page \d+\s*$
# Per-run statistics block
^execution time msec
^stmt / microsec
^stmt / millisec
^stmt / second
^stmts executed
^regenerations
^memory used \(bytes\)
^memory left \(bytes\)
